          "دفع": "Gave, handed over — implies a deliberate, authoritative act of giving",
          "دينار": "Gold coin (dinar), the standard gold currency of the Islamic world",
          "عيال": "Dependents, family members — those who depended on the slain for livelihood",
          "أصيب": "Was struck down, killed — in this context, martyred in battle"
        },
        "seo_question": "How did Imam al-Sadiq support the families of those who fought with Zayd ibn Ali?"
      },
